{"tid":482750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士風味香橙雪條","createTime":"2017-11-28T12:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T17:14:48.000Z","uid":137694,"like":169,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c99fadeddc849e5e2e96d5fca2255afc307700","tid":482750,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\nlindor朱古力<br />\n橙<br />\n廚師腸2條<br />\nm記杯<br />\n雪條棒<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202836_299ceed37a9a07133d54797a852f3e7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202836_299ceed37a9a07133d54797a852f3e7f.jpg&h=f7e437c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做法:<br />\n橙/廚師腸/朱古力一齊blend<br />\n倒入m記杯<br />\n雪條棒插入廚師腸<br />\n放入雪條漿中間, 然後放入冰格4小時<br />\n完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202920_9580485f4e109feb57b614be47fc499c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202920_9580485f4e109feb57b614be47fc499c.jpg&h=da642b97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202921_bd207b0a522831ba5109df297cb5221c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202921_bd207b0a522831ba5109df297cb5221c.jpg&h=09fc5e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202921_d092379f9cc8bbe0a3da2955cacb232a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202921_d092379f9cc8bbe0a3da2955cacb232a.jpg&h=a6d02a88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202922_d092379f9cc8bbe0a3da2955cacb232a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202922_d092379f9cc8bbe0a3da2955cacb232a.jpg&h=45999d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/202923_7fccdc586656d461bfc0aecf71661c99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F202923_7fccdc586656d461bfc0aecf71661c99.jpg&h=61eeadfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評分: 7/10<br />\n風景畫食評:<br />\n賣相係唔多好 同食屎無分別 不過食落係好好食<br />\n啖啖都有橙肉 條腸要含到最尾先食到 因為好撚硬 ["},{"pid":"4ad0ee9f605d45a3254ea92ae9ab028dd10f6618","tid":482750,"uid":71166,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1539a51d6e97a5c791cf94b476a2b7dc3f7c0b1","tid":482750,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf9e04ad0f6c2efd7dafb826b3be72ea94a3561","tid":482750,"uid":25378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b3d242eba1a9a8e27277d7445edd71bad4de58","tid":482750,"uid":133252,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"......."},{"pid":"c6b2fc22bc29ca608f2988b49e23f8df8a676bba","tid":482750,"uid":137694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欣宜真名上飲食台"},{"pid":"15b7b820e7cbc68d2d33c24219418b2fdf9e73d4","tid":482750,"uid":70718,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"幽默大師2018？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1726b1698c585d253695da3fccae396a21c14887","tid":482750,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s